{
  "stem": "11000.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And of course, once we got through the gate, and we were in the camp, the first thing we encountered was the selection.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this SS officer stood there with this little cane, and he decided that who goes to this side and who goes to that side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that's when-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] excuse me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] That's when my father went to one side, and I went to the other side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think that-- that was the last time I ever saw my dad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Then, of course, the selection consisted of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] twins.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "If there were any twins, they were separated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "If you had any tattoos on your body, you were selected.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We discovered after the war that these people were put to death and the tattoo skins were used for lamp shades for a overseer, a woman by the name of Ilse Koch.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And Ilse Koch was tried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Those lamp shades were used as evidence against her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "After that, we were-- we had to undress, naked, and they deloused us, which meant they had other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they used some kinds of disinfectant on your body, and you were shaved.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "All your hair on your body and your head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the Germans were always afraid of diseases.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were very particular.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They always made sure that you don't carry any like lice or were carriers of diseases.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then, of course, we got our number tattooed, our prison number, and we got, I remember, a striped jacket and striped pants and a cap, and we got two shoes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they weren't necessarily a left and a right one.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
